{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Watchword is a roguelike deck builder about playing words to beat increasingly difficult trials with rule-breaking synergies and combos.</strong>\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906730/extras/PiecesHighlight2.gif?t=1738356110\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A good vocabulary will certainly help, but it will mostly take careful planning and strategy to beat each trial. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Invent crazy new words and use special symbols to play a board that scores massively! Fill your bag and customize your collection of pieces.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906730/extras/BooksHighlight_no_matte.gif?t=1738356110\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Purchase books to ramp up your point scoring.\u00a0</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each book has a unique power that can help (or potentially hinder) depending on what pieces you use. Some books completely change the rules of the game. Explore, and discover  clever combinations!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906730/extras/UniqueRuns.gif?t=1738356110\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Journey through 3 regions to pass the final trial at the top of the city. In your travels you will come across run-changing encounters that will help determine your fate. Will you pass the trials and join the Watchguards?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906730/extras/Watchguard.gif?t=1738356110\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">100+ Unique book relics with unique powers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hundreds of piece variations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">20+ Watchguards each with their own set of challenges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">30+  run upgrades</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">100,000+ word base English dictionary\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Invent new words that work well with your build</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Check your stats and shoot for new high scores</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906730/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738356110","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906730/page.bg.jpg?t=1738356110","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906730/6b8ce10eaac42ba03c0e29183578f948b74f69cb/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738356110","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906730/6b8ce10eaac42ba03c0e29183578f948b74f69cb/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738356110","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Watchword is a roguelike deck builder about playing words to beat increasingly difficult trials with rule-breaking synergies and combos.</strong>\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2906730/extras/PiecesHighlight2.gif?t=1738356110\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A good vocabulary will certainly help, but it will mostly take careful planning and strategy to beat each trial. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Invent crazy new words and use special symbols to